<div class="row well">
  <div class="col-sm-8">
     <h3>
     Activate your account by connecting with stripe.  You will be asked to share information* with us. 
     Say yes. This enables you to accept credit cards on Karma Grove.  
     </h3>
   </div>

  <div class="col-sm-4">
  <%= link_to image_tag('stripe-blue@2x.png'), user_omniauth_authorize_path(:stripe_connect) %>
  </div>

  <% if current_user.role == "charity_admin" %>
    <div class="col-sm-8">
     <h5 class="notice">
     *We do not have access to any of your banking information stored in Stripe.  We receive a token that allows us to deposit our members' donated money into your account on a monthly basis.
     </h5>
     
   </div>
  <% else %>
    <div class="col-sm-8">
     <h5 class="notice">
     *We do not have access to any of your banking information stored in Stripe.  We receive a token that allows us to charge cards on your behalf, take a percentage for charity, and take <%= current_user.transaction_cost %> per transaction.  Stripe will deposit the money in your account in a few days. 
     </h5>
   </div>
   <% end %>
    
    <a href="http://www.businessinsider.com/stripe-the-invisible-5-billion-start-up-powering-the-internet-economy-2015-9" target="new"> What is stripe? </a>
 </div>